                                       Office of Truck Services




                                   CALIFORNIA AGENCIES

         For drivers license, weight fees, and vehicle registration, contact the
         Department of Motor Vehicles (DMV). Trip permits are no longer needed
         as of 12/31/01. For questions on the new registration procedures, call
         DMV at (916) 657-7971 or visit their web site at: http//www.dmv.ca.gov
         and go to the link "Commercial Vehicle Registration Act of 2001."

         For vehicle and terminal safety inspections, commercial vehicle
         enforcement facilities ("weigh stations"), hazardous material permits
         and routing or vehicle size and weight laws, contact the California
         Highway Patrol (CHP) at (916) 445-1865. http://www.chp.ca.gov/

         For truck weigh scale bypass (PrePass-TM) contact HELP, Inc. at
         1-800-PrePass. http://www.prepass.com

         For licensing of household goods carriers and motor carriers of
         passengers, i.e., tour buses, contact the California Public Utilities
         Commision at (800) 877-8867. http://www.cpuc.ca.gov/

         For fuel tax and sales tax payments contact the California Board of
         Equalization at (916) 322-9669. http://www.boe.ca.gov/
         For hauling animals, crops and produce contact the California
         Department of Food & Agriculture at (916) 654-0466.
         http://www.cdfa.ca.gov/phpps/pe/transport_animals_plants.htm


                          OFFICE OF TRUCK SERVICES

   The California Department of Transportation (DOT) Office of Truck
   Services web page is the portal to these DOT truck sites:
     * oversize/overweight permits (916) 654-6677,
       http://www.dot.ca.gov/hq/traffops/permits/
     * routes for trucks, tour buses, motorhomes, and motorsports events;
       public weigh scales (916) 654-5741,
       http://www.dot.ca.gov/hq/traffops/trksnwim/motion/motion.htm
     * truck weigh scale/inspection/enforcement facilities at
       http://www.dot.ca.gov/hq/traffops/trksnwim/weight/weight.htm
     * truck traffic data at (916) 654-3072,
       http://www.dot.ca.gov/hq/traffops

   STILL CAN'T FIND WHAT YOU NEED? Contact Caltrans staff at (916)
   654-5741, or by e-mail:

     Casey Robb: casey_robb@dot.ca.gov
     Manuel Fonseca: manuel_fonseca@dot.ca.gov





